do.com/kanji/煌\">kanshudo</a> | <a href=\"https://en.m.wiktionary.org/wiki/煌\">wiktionary</a> | <a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary_details/?word=煌\">purpleculture</a> | <a href=\"http://rtega.be/chmn/?c=煌\">rtega</a> | <a href=\"https://www.trainchinese.com/v2/search.php?searchWord=煌&tcLanguage=ru\">trainchinese</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=煌&tcLanguage=ru\">bkrs</a> | <a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=煌\">humanum</a> | <a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/煌\">Baido</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yw11.com/zidian/index/search/煌\">yw11</a> | <a href=\"plecoapi://x-callback-url/s?q=煌\">Pleco Search</a> | <a href=\"plecoapi://x-callback-url/s?mode=df&hw=煌&sec=dict&x-source=Anki\">Pleco</a>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"ch_with_same_pronounciation\">\n  <div class=\"pinyin\">huang2</div>\n  <div class=\"same-pronounciation\">\n    <div class=\"row row-hsk-3\"><span class=\"key\">HSK 3</span>: <span class=\"kanji\">黄</span>,<span class=\"kanji\">黃</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row row-hsk-6\"><span class=\"key\">HSK 6</span>: <span class=\"kanji\">煌</span></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"rtega_mnemonic\">\n  <table>\n    <tr>\n      <td>煌煌<a href=\"http://rtega.be/chmn/?reversec=煌\">R</a><a href=\"http://rtega.be/chmn/index.php?submit=4024\">S</a></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td>bright, shining, luminous</td>\n      <td>\n        <ul>\n          <li title=\"Reinaert Albrecht\">a royal <a href=\"http://rtega.be/chmn/?c=皇\">皇</a> fire <a href=\"http://rtega.be/chmn/?c=火\">火</a>: <i>bright</i> and <i>luminous</i></li>\n        </ul>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"purpleculture_info\">\n  <div>\n    <div><b>Chinese Definition:</b>\n      <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">皇</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">火</a></span> (fire) conveys the meaning.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"purpleculture_tree\">\n  <div class=\"tree\">\n    <ul>\n      <li><span class=\"str_def\">⿰</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">Left to right</span>\n        <ul>\n          <li><span class=\"str_def\"><a class=\"dictips\">火</a></span> <span class=\"str_py\">[ <a href=\"allsetlearning-huo3.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone3\">huǒ</a> ]</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">fire, flame; to burn; anger, rage</span></li>\n          <li><span class=\"str_def\"><a class=\"dictips\">皇</a></span> <span class=\"str_py\">[ <a href=\"allsetlearning-huang2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">huáng</a> ]</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">royal, imperial; ruler, superior</span></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<hr><span id=\"purpleculture_examples\">①光明，明亮：辉煌。星火煌煌。</span>\n<hr>\n<div>\n  <div><b>Chinese Definition:</b>\n    <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">皇</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">火</a></span> (fire) conveys the meaning.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div>HSK: 6</div>\n<div>Freq: 2276</div>\n<hr><span><span style=\"color:#1ce63d\">Kanshudo mnemonic:</span>the fire (<a href=\"/kanji/%E7%81%AB\">火</a>) emperor (<a href=\"/kanji/%E7%9A%87\">皇</a>) glitters</span>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Chinese</span>: Resplendent means magnificent. Here we have the fire emperor appearing as resplendent as any emporer in history.</div>\n<hr>\n<div><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Meaning:</span> resplendent<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Story:</span> Resplendent means magnificent. Here we have the fire emperor appearing as resplendent as any emporer in history.<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Kind:</span> both<br><img src=\"lf_29004.gif\"></div>\n<div>\n  <hr>\n</div>\n<hr><img src=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/kangxiArchaic.php?hash=8c67dc65fa3cb2adc1dbc00a5dad015e\"><br>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description\">金文從「 火 」，「 皇 」聲，本義是燈火輝煌，燦爛明亮。《說文》：「煌煌，煇也。从火皇聲。」(參段玉裁《說文解字注》)。偏旁「 火 」和「 皇 」金文或作上下結構，或作左右結構。 金文通假作「 鍠 」，用來形容鐘聲動聽。秦公鎛：「其音鍺鍺雝雝孔煌。」𪒠鎛：「龢平均煌」。</div>\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description_en\">Inscriptions from \" fire\", \" emperor\" sound, the original meaning is brilliant, brilliant and bright. \"Shuowen\": \"Huanghuang, Huiye. From the sound of the emperor of fire.\" (Refer to Duan Yucai's \"Shuowen Jiezi Annotation\"). The inscriptions \" Fire\" and \" Emperor\" in the radicals are either up-down structure or left-right structure. Clementine faked \" 锽\" to describe the sound of bells. Qin Gongpiao: \"The sound of germanium and germanium is Yong Yong, Konghuang and Huang.\"</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"hanziyuan\">\n  <div class=\"etymology-nav\" id=\"&#x714C;\">\n    <div class=\"alert alert-success etymology-alert m-0\" role=\"alert\"></div>\n    <div class=\"row bg-info border-purple border-top mx-0 row-eq-height\" id=\"E02384\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-4 p-0\">\n        <div class=\"p-1\">\n          <p></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in your browser 繁体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x714C;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in Unicode standard 繁体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=714C\" target=\"_blank\">U+714C</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-714C\"></p>\n          <p><b>Older traditional characters 旧繁体字/异体字:</b> Not exist</p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in your browser 简体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x714C;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in Unicode standard 简体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=714C\" target=\"_blank\">U+714C</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-714C\"></p>\n          <p><b>Main pronunciation 主要发音:</b> hu&#xE1;ng</p>\n          <p><b>Other pronunciations 其它发音:</b> Not exists.</p>\n          <p><b>Original meaning 本义:</b> Meaning bright.</p>\n          <p><b>English senses 英语理解:</b> bright, shining, luminous</p>\n          <p><b>Usage example 用法举例:</b> &#x714C;&#x714C; hu&#xE1;ng hu&#xE1;ng (brilliant)</p>\n          <p><b>Importance by frequency 常用频率:</b> 2290</p>\n          <p><b>Shuowen 说文解字:</b> &#x714C;&#x7147;&#x4E5F;&#x5F9E;&#x706B;&#x7687;&#x8072;</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Character decomposition 字形分解 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br>Compound &#x714C; &#xD;&#xA;from fire &#x706B; hu&#x1D2; and &#xD;&#xA;phonetic emperor-sun &#x7687; hu&#xE1;ng.</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Decomposition notes 字形分解说明 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Simplification rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Simplification rule explained <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Variant rule :</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Variant rule clarification <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Applied rules <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p><b>New font rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p><a target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-1 bg-primary col-md-9 col-sm-8 etymology-result\" id=\"etymologyCharacters\">\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known oracle characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known bronze characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span> Seal characters (1)</h3>\n        <ul class=\"list-inline list-unstyled\">\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-S07361.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span> Liushutong characters (6)</h3>\n        <ul class=\"list-inline list-unstyled\">\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L10172.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L10174.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L10175.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L10177.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>煌</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>煌<br>huáng<br>光明，明亮：辉煌。星火煌煌。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>煌</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［huáng］<br>［《廣韻》胡光切，平唐，匣。］<br>亦作“熿1”。<br>(1)明亮。<br>(2)火光。<br>(3)鲜明。<br>(4)盛；美。<br>(5)用同“惶”。参见“煌灼”。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>煌</span>字的英文翻译</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>◎ <b>煌</b><br>brilliant</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>煌</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【巳集中】【火字部】　煌； 康熙笔画：13； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0676.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页676第07</span></a><br>【唐韻】【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】?胡光切，音皇。【說文】煇也。【玉篇】光明也。【詩·陳風】東門之楊，明星煌煌。又【大雅】檀車煌煌。　又【廣韻】火狀。　又【前漢·地理志】敦煌郡武帝後元年，分酒泉置。【註】應劭曰：敦，大也。煌，盛也。　又【前漢·息夫躬傳】烏孫兩昆彌弱，卑爰疐强盛居彊煌之地。【註】是其國所都地名。　又通作皇。【詩·小雅】朱芾斯皇。【箋】皇，猶煌也。【集韻】或作熿?。　又【集韻】胡盲切，音橫。火光。　又【集韻】戸廣切，音幌。本作晄。明也。亦同熿爌。　又胡曠切，音愰。耀也。晄字原誤从先。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>煌</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>煌</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：1、煌熠，如光明灿烂；2、煌耀，闪耀，如辉煌。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">Bright<br>Basic explanation of words<br>Bright<br>huáng<br>Bright, bright: brilliant. Sparkle.<br>Bright<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［huáng］<br>[\"Guangyun\" Hu Guangqie, Ping Tang, Xie. ]<br>Also known as \"熿1\".<br>(1) Bright.<br>(2) Firelight.<br>(3) Bright.<br>(4) Sheng; beautiful.<br>(5) Use the same as \"anxious\". See \"Huang Zhuo\".<br>Bright<br>English translation of words<br>◎ Huang<br>brilliant<br>Bright<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Si Collection] [Fire Word Department] 　huang; Kangxi Strokes: 13; Page Number: Page 676 Page 07<br>[Tang Yun] [Ji Yun] [Yun Hui] [Zheng Yun]? Hu Guangqie, the emperor of sound. [Said Wen] Hui Ye. [Jade articles] Bright too. 【Poetry·Chen Feng】Yang from the East Gate, the star Huanghuang. And [Daya] Tan Che Huanghuang.　[Guang Yun] Fire shape.　[Pre-Han·Geography] The first year of Emperor Wu of Dunhuang County, it was placed in Jiuquan. [Note] Ying Shao said: Dun, Da Ye. Huang, Sheng Ye.　[Previous Han Xifu's Biography] Wusun and Liang Kun are weak, but humble and strong are strong and shining. [Note] It is the name of the capital of the country.　Through the emperor again. 【Poetry·Xiaoya】Emperor Zhu Fusi. 【Jian】Emperor, You Huang. [Ji Yun] Or Zuo Zhu?.　[Jiyun] Hu blindly cut, the sound is horizontal. Fire light.　[Jiyun] To Guangqie, Sound Horo. This is stunned. Ming Ye. The same is also the case.　 Hu Kuang cut again, sound stunned. Yaoya. The original word was wrong.<br>Bright<br>Source glyph<br>Bright<br>Name meaning<br>: 1. Brilliant, bright and brilliant; 2. Brilliant, shining, like brilliant.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274304786409.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274304786409.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148274304786409.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">煌<br>煌<br>金文<br>(huáng)<br>煌<br>一盖点燃的灯,在黑夜中发出煌煌亮光。<br>小篆<br>煌<br>“煌”字本义为光明、明亮,是一个象形字。在金文中,“煌”字下边为<br>一盏灯的形状,上面为“火”,即灯上有火,意味着光亮。小篆文中,“煌”字<br>的左边为“火”,代表字义;右边为“皇”,代表字音,即“煌”又成为一个形<br>声字了。“煌煌”常常连用,形容明亮辉煌的样子。现在,“煌”字还引申为光<br>彩鲜明的景象。<br>隶书<br>煌<br>楷体<br>公</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Яркий<br>Яркий<br>(хуан)<br>Яркий<br>Зажженная лампа ярко светилась в темноте ночи.<br>Яркий<br>Первоначальное значение слова «хуан» - яркое и яркое, и это пиктографический символ.<br>В бронзовых надписях нижняя часть слова «хуан» имеет форму лампы, а верхняя часть - «огонь», что означает, что на лампе горит огонь, что означает свет.<br>В письме маленькой печати левая сторона символа «хуан» - «火», которая представляет значение слова; правая сторона - «皇», которая представляет звук иероглифа, то есть «хуан». снова стал пиктофонетическим персонажем.<br>«Хуанхуан» часто используется вместе, чтобы описать яркую и блестящую внешность.<br>Теперь слово «хуан» также распространяется на яркую и яркую сцену.<br>Яркий<br>Курсив<br>общественный</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">huáng</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong><i> прил.</i></div>\n  <div>светлый, блестящий, ослепительный; великолепный</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">煌星 яркая звезда</span></div>\n  <div><strong>II</strong><i> гл.</i></div>\n  <div>сверкать, сиять</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=煌\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=煌&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=煌\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=煌\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=煌\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/煌\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=煌\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/煌\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=煌&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#煌\">Char lookup site</a></p>\n<div class=\"notes optional small\">火 (огонь), 王 (монарх), 白 (белый)</div>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"火","pinyins":["Huo3","huo3"]},{"glyph":"皇","pinyins":["Huang2"]}]}